headline.print_headline: Putin in Sochi: a Disciplined Show
headline.main: Putin in Sochi: a Disciplined Show

lead_paragraph: So far during the Winter Olympics, Vladimir Putin hasn't shown off his pecs, scuba-dived to a treasure site or engaged in any sort of the he-man stunts he's known for.
